messages.message: Anyone know where the launcher in a workspace gets its list of apps from? It seems like it uses a different pathway than when you are in an app

i believe in the filesystem it gets the list from what apps you can access on the default `Instabase Drive` . If you have access to apps on other drives but not the `Instabase Drive` , it won’t show them.
Ah nvm I think I found my issue… looks like they use the same pathway, but apps get their list of apps from apps-server, while drive gets its apps from webapp
